50|$|Two main {{versions}} {{exist as}} to <b>the</b> <b>Hopi's</b> emergence into <b>the</b> present Fourth World. The more prevalent is that Spider Grandmother caused a hollow reed (or bamboo) {{to grow into}} the sky, and it emerged in the Fourth World at the sipapu. The people then climbed up the reed into this world, emerging from the sipapu. The location of the sipapu is given as in the Grand Canyon.|$|R
